snippet.title: World in Conflict Soviet Assault Trailer
snippet.description:
About World in Conflict Soviet Assault: 
The game that was universally hailed as Strategy Game of the Year 2007 returns with all new content! World In Conflict Soviet Assault features six new single player missions and eight new multiplayer maps all played from the perspective of the Soviet side of the conflict.
